						               													<description>Expansion for the Discovery Games edition of Source of the Nile.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This supplement clarifies many rules from Source of the Nile, and introduces many new and optional rules including:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Customizing not only the explorer but EVERY guide, bearer and askari with individual skills, stregnths, and weaknesses&amp;#10;     Rules for lady explorers&amp;#10;     Rules for developments in weapon technology, to even up the odds against the heathen savages&amp;#10;     Rules for the slave trade, and encounters with slave raiders&amp;#10;     Cape Colony and the Boers&amp;#10;     Rules for shooting the rapids and going over cataracts&amp;#10;     A name generator for tribes&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;While this supplement was intended for the Discovery Games edition, with a little tweaking, it is serviceable for use with the Avalon Hill edition, particularly if you use the &amp;quot;game 2&amp;quot; ruleset. Using all of these rules will greatly increase the complexity of the game, but if you can handle it all, it is a very rewarding and involved simulation of an African adventure.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
